creator: Pi Games Studio
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to our puppy pet salon care game.
Enjoy all pet daycare activities with amazing levels.
Experience babysitting with cute little puppy and learn all daycare manners.

Start your day by giving nice hot bubble bath to little puppy, feed him with yummy food, help him in making nice house to stay then decorate it with your creativity.

While playing puppy may get hurt so take very good care of him and give him some primary medical treatment in case of injury.

Always keep your pet upto date and dress him up with cute dresses and accessories

creator: Pi Games Studio
descriptionHtml:
If you are a dog lover, Welcome to our puppy care guide game.

Experience pet babysitting activities with little puppies.

Start your day by giving a nice hot bubble bath to the little puppy, feed him with yummy food, help him in making a nice house to stay then decorate it with your creativity.


Puppy is so dirty playing all day on street. Clean him and wash him properly with pet soaps.
But there is a problem with the water tank. Fix the pipes in tanks and allow water to flow easily.
Enjoy a bubble bath with a cute little puppy.

Puppy teeth are hurting. Let’s help him in cleaning teeth and kill the germs bacteria. Same as human teeth treatment, remove all the cavities from the puppy mouth.

While playing puppy got injured and has many cuts. Apply the cream on the cuts and put bandaid for faster recovery.
Learn all the medical tools used in first aid treatment. Make sure the little puppy feels less pain.


Make some yummy food and feed the baby pet puppy. You will get a chance to cook something for a puppy animal.
Make sure he eats well and gets enough energy for playing.


Even puppy wants their house clean and tidy. As we keep our house clean and do all household chores by ourselves, help pet puppy to keep their place hygiene.
Collect all the dirt and clean floors and walls.


Build a pet house with all types of wood materials and screw fittings. A puppy needs some rest, so let us help him in making a small pet house.
Choose the color for a house you want and make an amazing nameplate for a puppy house.


Along with puppy daycare activities, you can play multiple mini-games for fun. Teach cute puppies how to jump and pass through obstacles. Also, there is a water gun to enjoy and make the puppy happy.


Always keep your pet up to date and dress him up with cute dresses and accessories. You will get an amazing collection of puppy dresses, shoes, caps, goggles, etc.

creator: Pi Games Studio
descriptionHtml:
Girls and boys, we are so excited to welcome you to the Puppy Care Salon Babysitting Game! It's going to be a blast taking care of these adorable puppies. Get ready for some fun and exciting times ahead! Let's get started!

If you are a canine enthusiast, you are in the right place! Our puppy care guide game will give you the opportunity to experience the joys of pet babysitting. To begin your day, give the puppy a warm bath with pet soap to get them all cleaned up from playing outside all day. There may be some issues with the water tank, so you'll have to fix the pipes to let the water flow freely. Enjoy the bubble bath with your new furry friend!
The puppy's teeth may be in need of a cleaning, so you can help them out by removing any cavities and killing off any germs and bacteria. If the pup has any cuts or injuries, make sure to apply the cream and put a bandaid on for faster recovery. You can learn all the medical tools used in first aid treatment and make sure the puppy feels as little pain as possible.
Don't forget to make some yummy food for the puppy and feed them to make sure they have enough energy for playing. Make sure to keep their house clean and tidy as well. All in all, you will have a great time taking care of a pet puppy!

We should keep our home tidy and do all the household duties ourselves, as well as helping our pup stay hygienic. We should collect all the dirt and dirtiness, cleaning floors and walls. We can construct a pet house with a variety of wood materials and screw fastenings. Our puppy requires some rest, so let's assist them in creating a little pet house. We can select the color of the home we want and make a wonderful nameplate for the puppy house. In addition to puppy daycare activities, we can play multiple mini-games for amusement. We can teach our cute puppies how to jump and move through hurdles. There is also a water gun to relish and make the puppy joyful. We should always keep our pet up to date and dress them up with lovely dresses and accessories. We will obtain a great selection of puppy dresses, shoes, caps, goggles, etc.

descriptionHtml:
Are you a pet lover looking for fun and interactive games to play with your furry friend? Look no further than these amazing pet games that are sure to provide hours of entertainment for both you and your beloved pet.

First up is the Amazing Bath Game for Pet. This game allows you to give your pet a virtual bath, complete with soap, shampoo, and even a rubber duck! Your pet will love splashing around in the water, and you'll love the ease of cleaning up your pet without making a mess in your home.

Next, we have the Beautiful Dressing for little dog Dress up game. This game is perfect for those who love to dress up their pets in adorable outfits. Choose from a variety of clothing options, including hats, scarves, and even sunglasses, to create a unique and stylish look for your furry friend.

For those who love to pamper their pets, the Puppy Salon game is a must-play. This game allows you to give your pet a full makeover, including a haircut, nail trim, and even a facial. Your pet will feel like a true VIP after a visit to this virtual salon.

If your pet is feeling under the weather, the Puppy Doctor game is the perfect way to give them the care they need. This game allows you to play the role of a veterinarian, diagnosing and treating a variety of ailments to help your pet feel better in no time.

Finally, for those who dream of creating the perfect home for their pet, the Dog Home Making game is a must-try. This game allows you to design and decorate a virtual home for your pet, complete with furniture, toys, and even a backyard for your pet to play in.

Whether you're looking for a fun way to bond with your pet or simply want to keep them entertained, these amazing pet games are sure to provide hours of fun and excitement for both you and your furry friend.
